source.name: Industry Highlight: Real Estate, Rental and Leasing Industry
source.description: "Industry Profiles" is a series on the largest industries in Boston. They contain facts on employment, major employers, education, and more. This report highlights Boston's Real Estate, Rental and Leasing industry.
